		<main> 
			<h1>Projects I Made In Illustrator</h1>
			<p>Below are my creative projects from my Adobe Illustrator college course. In the class I learned the software through the 16 lessons from the 2020 version of Adobe Illustrator,'classroom in a book'. I used the techniques from thoughs lesson to create coasters, halloween and event posters, and a business card.</p>
			
			<h2>Coasters</h2>
			<p>The coaster design was my first project for the class. I did the changes in the four seasons from my grandmas home. a place that is very peaceful to me.</p>
			<div class="container-fluid">
				<div class="row">
					<div class="col-sm-6">
						<img class="coaster img-fluid" src="images/coaster.png" alt="four circles with images inside representing the four seasons" height="613" width="762" >
					</div>
					<h2>Business Card</h2>
					<p> The business card logo was the final project for the class. I imaged a long haired cat girl with her hair blowing in the wind over her face. It turned into a ghostly image, which I quite like.</p>
					<div class="col-sm-6">
						<img class="card img-fluid" src="images/business-card.jpg" alt="rectangular grid of ten sections in two columes with words and a ghostly girl image on a dark blue background" height="612" width="792" >
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
